snippet.title: Keylocker - Official Announcement Trailer | ID@Xbox April 2024
snippet.description:
Explore the surreal, colorful world of Keylocker and meet the characters, see combat, and more in this trailer for the turn-based rhythm JRPG, as revealed during ID@Xbox April 2024. Keylocker will be available in summer 2024 on Xbox Series X/S, (PS5) PlayStation 5, Nintendo Switch, and Steam.

In the dystopian world of Saturn, where music has been banned for over a century, rebellion brews beneath the surface. You will play as Bobo, a daring Singer determined to fight for Saturn's freedom and restore music to the silent world.

#IGN #Xbox
